window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>“You want me to find you a wife?”</b></p> <p><b>“No. I want you to be my wife.” </b></p> <p>Garrett Song is this close to taking the reins of his family’s LA fashion empire...until the Song matriarch insists he marries her handpicked bride first. To block her matchmaking, he recruits Natalie Sobol to pose as his wife. She needs a fake spouse as badly as he does. But when passion burns down their chaste agreement, the flames could destroy them all....</p>"; 
